---
source: crates/loom/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: "loom_help(&[\"gate\", \"review\"])"
---
Run criterion-attached judges and the LLM rubric

Usage: loom gate review [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --files <PATH>...     Scope to verifiers whose declared inputs intersect this file set
  -w, --workspace <PATH>    Workspace root. Defaults to the current working directory
  -A, --agent <BACKEND>     Override the agent backend for this invocation [possible values: claude, pi]
      --target <TARGET>     Run annotations whose target exactly matches this string
      --diff <RANGE>        Scope to a git diff range
      --tree                Scope to every file in the workspace
  -b, --bead <ID>           Attach review context to an explicit diff scope
      --verify-exit <CODE>  Exit code of a prior `loom gate verify --diff <range>` run. Threaded from `loom loop`'s molecule-completion handoff so the push gate's four-condition AND can refuse on a non-zero verify exit per FR9 condition 2
  -h, --help                Print help
